title: Rammstein Live 2010/2013 DVD9 Proshot
description:
This is a DVD i made including all Rammstein songs recorded professionally in 2010 and 2013. It also contains 4 interviews with some of the Rammstein members.

Since this is a unofficial DVD made from various video files and formats, don't expect an insane crystal clear HD image; I'm in the proccess of making a Blu-Ray version of this with nearly perfect BR quality, as soon as i got my software issues fixed.

While waiting for the next official live DVD from Rammstein, I really hope fans can enjoy this one in the meantime! :)
